-- Toyota mulling more North American capacity
-- 
-- Thu Jan 4, 2007 11:26am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/01/04/us-toyota-capacity-n-america-idUSN0419288320070104

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Corp.( 7203.T ) is considering expanding its manufacturing capacity in North America and is currently reviewing sites, spokesman Dan Sieger said on Thursday. 

 "We are looking at sites," he said, but declined to reveal details.